OL,3,CGrolsch drops alcohol content amid
OL,4,Csales slump and tax rules on weaker
OL,5,Cbrews
OL,7,FGrolsch Premium Pilsner has had its
OL,8,Falcohol content slashed to 3.4%
OL,9,Falcohol by volume (abv) in the UK amid
OL,10,Fshrinking sales and discounted tax
OL,11,Frules on weaker brews.
OL,13,FThe pilsner beer, which is sold with a
OL,14,F5% abv in Europe, had already been
OL,15,Frelaunched by Asahi in the UK with a
OL,16,Fabv of 4% in 2020.
OL,18,FNow, amid a further fall in demand,
OL,19,Fbosses at Asahi have again slashed the
OL,20,Falcohol content carried by the beer.
