OL,7,FThe decision will reportedly save
OL,8,FAsahi UK 23p in excise duty per 440ml
OL,9,Fcan of Grolsch sold.
OL,11,FSpeaking to The Grocer, Asahi said it
OL,12,Fhad "learnt a lot" about "consumer
OL,13,Fpreferences and evolving consumption
OL,14,Ftrends," and that the brewer is
OL,15,F"confident this still delivers an
OL,16,Fexcellent premium beer that will
OL,17,Fappeal to a broad range of consumers."
