OL,7,FLast year, the government rejigged how
OL,8,Falcohol was taxed and introduced a
OL,9,Fnumber of increases for higher abv
OL,10,Fdrinks and cuts for lower abv products.
OL,12,FAnd, just over a week away from the
OL,13,Fnew Labour government's first budget,
OL,14,Fit has been reported that Chancellor
OL,15,FRachel Reeves could make further
OL,16,Fchanges to the way alcohol duty is
OL,17,Fcalculated.
OL,19,FAlcohol duty rises each year in line
OL,20,Fwith inflation, unless the chancellor
OL,21,Fmakes the decision to freeze it.
