OL,7,FCurrently facing down a #22 billion
OL,8,Fblackhole, Reeves has said she is
OL,9,Fprepared to make tough decisions when
OL,10,Fconcerning the public purse strings -
OL,11,Fand forecasts that a raise in alcohol
OL,12,Fduty would raise an extra #800 million
OL,13,Fcould feature as part of Reeves' plans
OL,14,Fto restore public finances.
OL,16,FPotentially further incentivizing
OL,17,Fbrewers to lower alcohol content while
OL,18,Fkeeping prices the same, a phenomenon
OL,19,Fthat has been dubbed "drinkflation".
